WOrking APache Spark in Terminal 

step 1: 

java --version
sudo apt install default-jdk

Step 2:

Apache Spark install go to location: https://www.apache.org/dyn/closer.lua/spark/spark-3.5.1/spark-3.5.1-bin-hadoop3.tgz

seperate folder spark / and extract that using tar or right click

Go to the that folder ex: home/spark/----- ls-----ls -lrt

commands : tar -xvzf spark-3.5.1-bin-hadoop3.tgz/// ls -lrt

step 3:

PATH="/usr/local/sbin:/usr/local/bin:/usr/sbin:/usr/bin:/sbin:/bin:/usr/games:/usr/local/games:/snap/bin"
JAVA_HOMEPATH="/usr/lib/jvm/java-11-openjdk-amd64"


SPARK_HOME=/Desktop/Spark_demo/spark-3.5.1-bin-hadoop3
PATH=$PATH:$SPARK_HOME/bin:$SPARK_HOME/sbin
